      "content": "That framing makes sense, but I'm worried if we just use words like \"strategic investment,\" the analysts are going to dig into the actual CAC numbers. They'll see the specific percentage increase and call us out on it. Should we just include the full breakdown of the CAC in the summary slides, or is there a better way to handle those specific figures?",
